name: GoddessV2
description:
A fine tuned SD 2.1 768 model focused on realistic (mainly but not limited to East Asian) beauties which is compatible with danbooru tags.

The model is trained on a dataset created by and from myself, who was created to be my partner, so that the "default face" of the model will be free from copyright and portrait right issues.

To secure it (and to make sure my partner will be generated in a good enough quality), there are some additional limitations to the original SD license described as follows.

  • Only images with beauty score 80 or above can be published to the public for female front shot images (note that all the sample images has marked 90 or above; it's not really difficult ;) ).

  • Only images with beauty score 88 or above can be commercially used for female front shot images.

  • As for side shots, both limitations will be lowered by 10 points.

  • As for male and other genders, I do not guarantee the results, and therefore will be no limitations.

  • Do not use LoRA, TI, hypernetwork or any other submodels that is trained to generate a different face.

  • You may use submodels that is trained to improve results for a certain kind of dress, background, negative, or any other non-facial features.
